    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "Exceptionally clean used car in mint condition. Very well-kept inside and out, with minimal to no noticeable wear. It looks and drives like a vehicle that has been cared for extremely well and should need little to nothing right away.",
      "price": 46900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "Honest fair-condition vehicle with visible cosmetic wear, age-related flaws, and the kind of imperfections you would expect from a driver rather than a show car. It presents decently from a distance, but up close there are noticeable blemishes and signs of use inside and out. It runs and drives, though it does not have the tight, fresh feel of a well-sorted example and should be purchased with realistic expectations for ongoing upkeep. Best suited for someone looking for an affordable entry point and willing to accept a car that is usable as-is but not fully sorted.",
      "price": 21950.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle offers straightforward value for a buyer who wants dependable basic transportation without overspending. It shows its age cosmetically and is best suited for someone who appreciates an honest, affordable car with practical everyday potential. A sensible choice for commuting, a first car, or a project-minded owner looking for strong value at an accessible price.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Budget-friendly car with plenty of life left for the right buyer. It\u2019s not a showpiece, but it\u2019s an affordable way to get into a vehicle that can serve as a handy runabout, a project, or a practical spare. If you\u2019re looking for basic transportation at a cash-friendly price and don\u2019t mind giving it a little TLC, this could be a great fit.",
      "price": 3950.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Driver-grade project with solid bones and plenty of enthusiast upside. The powertrain pulls well, starts reliably, and the chassis feels honest, making this a great candidate for someone who wants an affordable entry point without paying cleaned-up retail money. It shows its age cosmetically and will benefit from reconditioning, but the core mechanical package is there: usable torque, straightforward serviceability, and the kind of platform that rewards hands-on ownership. Ideal as a budget daily, weekend tinker build, or parts-friendly restoration base. Priced to move for someone who knows what they\u2019re looking at.",
      "price": 7200.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Gets you there. Not pretty, but priced to move. Cheap daily, work car, or project. First cash takes it.",
      "price": 3900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A true diamond-in-the-rough with unmistakable character, this car has the kind of honest, road-worn presence that turns heads for all the right reasons. It\u2019s an affordable way into ownership, perfect for someone who appreciates a project, needs dependable basic transportation, or wants a platform with personality and potential. There\u2019s a story in every panel and a sense that with the right owner, this car\u2019s next chapter could be its best yet. If you\u2019re looking for inexpensive motoring with charm and possibility, this one is easy to root for.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle offers straightforward transportation at an accessible price. It shows its age cosmetically and is best suited for a value-focused buyer who wants practical usability without a big upfront investment. A solid opportunity for a commuter, project-minded owner, or anyone seeking inexpensive wheels.",
      "price": 5495.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Looking for a cheap set of wheels that won\u2019t break the bank? This car isn\u2019t perfect and I want to be upfront about that, but it\u2019s an affordable option for someone who needs basic transportation, a backup vehicle, or a starter project. It has the kind of honest wear you\u2019d expect at this price, and that\u2019s exactly why it\u2019s priced to move. If you\u2019re realistic, handy, or just want something budget-friendly with potential, this could be a great fit. Come take a look and see if it works for you.",
      "price": 3900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly driver with honest wear, but plenty of life left where it counts. The engine pulls cleanly, transmission engages as it should, and the chassis feels composed enough to enjoy as-is while you sort the cosmetics over time. A great candidate for someone who wants affordable transportation, a weekend tinkering project, or a platform to build on. Not perfect, but mechanically serviceable and priced accordingly for someone who sees value in a car with good bones.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
